      "role": "user",
      "content": "gotcha. so the ridges on the rebar are what make it stick. i guess if a building is huge, they have to put a lot of that stuff deep inside the concrete. is there any risk of things going wrong inside the structure where you can't see it, like if the metal reacts with the concrete or something?",
